rows.label: qst201901_0010
rows.name:
You know, I almost missed being
a million miles from nowhere.

rows.label: qst201901_0020
rows.name:
Rinne, why did you take us all the
way out here?

rows.label: qst201901_0030
rows.name: Hahah! Have you no eyes in your heads, peons?

rows.label: qst201901_0040
rows.name:
Behold! These magnificent white sands...
This crystal clear lake...

rows.label: qst201901_0050
rows.name:
And the mansion at the lakeside...
What better place for the perfect vacation?

rows.label: qst201901_0060
rows.name:
Is this not the summer paradise that you longed for?! The dream
island destination that makes you the envy of your peers?!

rows.label: qst201901_0070
rows.name: Wait... Wh-wh-wh-why is there absolutely nothing here?!?!

rows.label: qst201901_0080
rows.name: And...to...think...

rows.label: qst201901_0090
rows.name:
It cost us a million gold to become
the owner of this island...

rows.label: qst201901_0100
rows.name: A million?!

rows.label: qst201901_0110
rows.name:
You mean to say you BOUGHT
this island?!

rows.label: qst201901_0120
rows.name: We saved up the money over a long period of time...

rows.label: qst201901_0130
rows.name:
We had intended to purchase an opulent mansion on a small
cozy island. And then...

rows.label: qst201901_0140
rows.name:
We would gather the loveliest women from around
the world to our paradise...

rows.label: qst201901_0150
rows.name:
Eat, drink and be merry...
It was our dream come true...

rows.label: qst201901_0160
rows.name:
What are we to do with this dinky, dreary, desolate
excuse for a landmass...

rows.label: qst201901_0170
rows.name: Looks like you've been had.

rows.label: qst201901_0180
rows.name: Yep yep. It clear that Rinne tricked!

rows.label: qst201901_0190
rows.name:
You are indeed correct.
We have been well and truly deceived.

rows.label: qst201901_0200
rows.name:
That Superbian black-feathered fool...
He robbed us of our money and made off with it!

rows.label: qst201901_0210
rows.name: Black-feathered fool?

rows.label: qst201901_0220
rows.name: Could it have been a Nopon merchant?

rows.label: qst201901_0230
rows.name: I see. It seems you can identify the perpetrator.

rows.label: qst201901_0240
rows.name: That makes things simple.

rows.label: qst201901_0250
rows.name:
Right! All we've gotta do is get
the money back from them!

rows.label: qst201901_0260
rows.name: Come on, cheer up!

rows.label: qst201901_0270
rows.name: Nia, Meleph, Kagutsuchi...

rows.label: qst201901_0280
rows.name: You will lend us your aid?

rows.label: qst201901_0290
rows.name: Goes without saying really.

rows.label: qst201901_0300
rows.name:
If we leave this merchant to his own devices,
there are sure to be more victims.

rows.label: qst201901_0310
rows.name: We should get this over with as quickly as possible.

rows.label: qst201901_0320
rows.name: Ohh, our beloved friends...

rows.label: qst201901_0330
rows.name: You alone would treat us with such kindness...

rows.label: qst201901_0340
rows.name:
As proof of our gratitude, let us welcome you into
the uppermost echelons of our entourage!

rows.label: qst201901_0350
rows.name: ...Nah, you're all right there.

rows.label: qst201901_0360
rows.name:
Indeed... I don't think I'm befitting
of such a position.

rows.label: qst201901_0370
rows.name: Agreed. It's the thought that counts.

rows.label: qst201901_0380
rows.name: 'Tis a shame, truly.

rows.label: qst201901_0390
rows.name:
But it matters not.
That impudent, feathered fool, on the other hand...!

rows.label: qst201901_0400
rows.name:
How dare that dirty, dopey-looking creature
toy with our delicate feelings!

rows.label: qst201901_0410
rows.name: Justice will be served, we swear!

rows.label: qst201901_0420
rows.name:
Come, beloved friends! Let us make
for Alba Margen, the imperial capital!

rows.label: qst201901_0430
rows.name: Ah, peons and beasts may carry the luggage.

rows.label: qst201901_0440
rows.name: We expect you to pull your weight!

rows.label: qst201901_0450
rows.name: Excuse me?!
